Data exploring and preprocessing

Pre-processing of the data.

ucldf = read.csv("/Users/clairehe/Desktop/UEFA_CL_Player_stats.csv", header=T)
head(ucldf)


na_plot <- function(df){
  data <- as.matrix(is.na(df))
  for (cols in 1:length(ncol)){
    data[,cols]<- as.integer(data[,cols])
  }
  heatmap(data,Colv = NA, Rowv = NA, scale="column")
}

na_plot(ucldf)

Systematic missing values for 1664 in League season 13/14 and 14/15 due to data collection. Look for data without missing values caused by data collection. Let’s first remove these as we are interested in predicting the rating of player given their season’s performance in the Champion’s league.
